column5: Got out early this morning and started fishing around 8.Was kinda slow but picked up.Went for northern pike and had a bigger jigging lure on and saw some larger fish on sonar up under the ice but couldn't get them to bite except one 30+" pike.Had a jig and minnow going in the other hole a probably caught around 30 eater sized walleyes.They all went back as I wasn't keeping any today.Pike went back to.No cleaning today.
